# MINIMAL FLEXT-LDAP CONFIGURATION
# All other settings use smart defaults from FlextCore.Constants
#
# FlextLdapConfig automatically:
# - Detects server capabilities
# - Uses FlextCore.Constants for all timeouts, pools, limits
# - Configures optimal SSL/TLS settings
# - Enables connection pooling with smart defaults
# - Auto-configures retry and caching
#
# ONLY 3 REQUIRED VARIABLES for local testing:

FLEXT_LDAP_CONNECTION__PORT=3390
# Connection (auto-detects port, SSL, timeouts from server)
FLEXT_LDAP_CONNECTION__SERVER=localhost

# Authentication (use empty/remove for anonymous bind)
FLEXT_LDAP_AUTH__BIND_DN=cn=admin,dc=flext,dc=local
FLEXT_LDAP_AUTH__BIND_PASSWORD=admin123

# OPTIONAL - Only if you need to override auto-detection:
# FLEXT_LDAP_SEARCH__BASE_DN=dc=flext,dc=local  # Auto-detected from server
# FLEXT_LDAP_CONNECTION__USE_SSL=false  # Auto-detected from server URI
# FLEXT_LDAP_LOGGING__LOG_LEVEL=DEBUG   # Only for debugging

# That's it! FlextCore.Config handles the rest automatically.
